<doc id="196116" wikidata="Q11871381" url="?curid=196116" title="Chinese chess (disambiguation)">
<text>Chinese chess primarily refers to xiangqi, a two-player Chinese game in a family of strategic board games of which Western chess, Indian chaturanga, Japanese shogi, and the more similar Korean janggi are also members. This may also refer to:

*Chess in China (international, western, chess)
*Chinese Chess Association

